{
  "stem": "25544.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was always active, you know, when he was young.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so they took us over to cross the border to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they brought us to a certain point and then we had to get off the trucks and we had to cross, you know, so we shouldn't be caught by the guards.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, they were-- you know, they were probably bribed or whatever, but there was always the chance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you came to a certain point, and then-- and I remember, in the truck, there was somebody throwing up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was so sick that when I walked out-- I was a young woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was 21 years old, and I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So my-- my-- my husband-- and he found a cousin after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was the only survivor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Her parents perished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had to-- like, you know, I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had  to carry me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was so sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we came into Czechoslovakia in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we stayed over there, like, for a day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then they took us-- we were going to go as Greek Jews, you know, because we had to go through the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So they put us in, again, in cattle cars and they brought us into Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to talk because the Russians came in to count-- I guess, they paid them off by the head, whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they told-- and everybody spoke Russian, the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they told us not to say anything, just to pretend that we don't understand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were counting how many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we came to Austria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was about 12,000 people in that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lintz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called Lintz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
